Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.81,0:00:40.11,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}提著稍有些汙漬的行李包
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.11,0:00:43.11,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}什麼也不知道 從天空降落
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.11,0:00:45.93,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}從地圖的正對面 在這裡登場
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.93,0:00:48.62,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}在這夢中憧憬的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.62,0:00:51.34,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Yea Yea Yea
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.34,0:00:54.33,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\be1}The Rock City Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.33,0:00:57.31,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Yea Yea Yea
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.31,0:01:00.36,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\be1}The Rock City Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.76,0:01:04.56,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Oh baby 跳吧 跳吧 跳越牆壁 With my guitar
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.56,0:01:07.21,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}直到傳達到為止 oh yeah 唱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.21,0:01:09.92,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Just music 僅僅只是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.92,0:01:12.70,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}奉獻給你喔 oh yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.70,0:01:16.32,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}真的有很多相同點嗎? With my guitar
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.32,0:01:19.33,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}邊探索 Yea 邊唱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.33,0:01:22.08,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Just love 僅僅只是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.08,0:01:24.66,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}追趕上 be free!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.66,0:01:28.26,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}My 完美夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.43,0:01:42.99,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}睡時也好醒時也好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.99,0:01:46.21,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be1}把夢作為同伴哦 Yea
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.21,0:01:47.79,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\be1}I wanna believe the singing on beat
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.79,0:01:49.48,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\be1}most recently is like recess for me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.48,0:01:50.73,OP_EN,,0,0,0,,{\be1}pretty pretty please,no birds and the bees
